{"tid":1124570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"停職警長涉偷32元物品　自辯情緒受困案發時腦海一片空白","createTime":"2019-04-25T06:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T11:15:16.000Z","uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"534b94f416c9f6df0abc149110c744a233ec2e55","tid":1124570,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T06:14:05.000Z","msg":"已停職警長被指於去年在深水埗一間特賣店內，偷取4件共值32元物品。他早前否認一項盜竊罪，案件今在西九龍法院續審。警長早前被裁定表證成立，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他今自辯稱因2017年時遭廉正公署落案起訴，因而壓力過大情緒受困擾，案發時「腦海一片空白」無意識地將貨件放入環保袋內，而非存心偷竊。</span></span>警長妻子亦出庭作供，證明警長案發前精神狀況不好，甚至會在8號風球下強逼自己跑步等，最終用了近一年時間才說服他到精神科求診。<br />\n<br />\n現時仍被停職51歲被告張家輝供稱，2015年因有人舉報，10月時被廉正公署拘捕，直到2017年10月才正式被起訴2項公職人員行為失當罪。雖然案件在去年10月審結，他獲判無罪，辯方資深大律師郭棟明亦呈上多項文件，證明被告當時身陷「冤案」；被告則指自己在該兩年間壓力非常大、經常失眠、飲酒、體重更急降20磅。<br />\n<br />\n本案於去年5月18日發生，當時廉署案件仍未開審，但他因壓力過大，心神恍惚，每日會「周街行到流連忘返」，直至妻子著他回家。他其時仍未覺自己情緒有問題，但在高買案後就特別自責，甚至會不能自控地哭泣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/986830-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%81%9C%E8%81%B7%E8%AD%A6%E9%95%B7%E6%B6%89%E5%81%B732%E5%85%83%E7%89%A9%E5%93%81+%E8%87%AA%E8%BE%AF%E6%83%85%E7%B7%92%E5%8F%97%E5%9B%B0%E6%A1%88%E7%99%BC%E6%99%82%E8%85%A6%E6%B5%B7%E4%B8%80%E7%89%87%E7%A9%BA%E7%99%BD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F986830-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E5%2581%259C%25E8%2581%25B7%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%2581%25B732%25E5%2585%2583%25E7%2589%25A9%25E5%2593%2581%2B%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2583%2585%25E7%25B7%2592%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%259B%25B0%25E6%25A1%2588%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2599%2582%25E8%2585%25A6%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%2589%2587%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E7%2599%25BD&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5Sc2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=f9e9478e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F986830-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E5%2581%259C%25E8%2581%25B7%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%2581%25B732%25E5%2585%2583%25E7%2589%25A9%25E5%2593%2581%2B%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2583%2585%25E7%25B7%2592%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%259B%25B0%25E6%25A1%2588%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2599%2582%25E8%2585%25A6%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%2589%2587%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E7%2599%25BD&h=9025b304\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/986830-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%81%9C%E8%81%B7%E8%AD%A6%E9%95%B7%E6%B6%89%E5%81%B732%E5%85%83%E7%89%A9%E5%93%81+%E8%87%AA%E8%BE%AF%E6%83%85%E7%B7%92%E5%8F%97%E5%9B%B0%E6%A1%88%E7%99%BC%E6%99%82%E8%85%A6%E6%B5%B7%E4%B8%80%E7%89%87%E7%A9%BA%E7%99%BD</a><br />\n<br />\n笑死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"813ef3d5b319c5efd4850a426dbac2a4b1b5150f","tid":1124570,"uid":9013,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T06:20:40.000Z","msg":"叫火雞姐學下人啦，人地32蚊偷就係偷，理得你咩原因"},{"pid":"fc19c9c87326ba2c91bb38c6cfaf485f91a6a66f","tid":1124570,"uid":237562,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T06:23:43.000Z","msg":"應該是佔中影響到佢貪污啫"},{"pid":"5cb4f9f12e2cf3af9140dd29e020cc752405a7f9","tid":1124570,"uid":14816,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T06:31:31.000Z","msg":"渣渣輝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d0e3163a198f4416bd285528a898594ff609fb","tid":1124570,"uid":189336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T06:33:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e0a9810914b72ed92f7c730532259dc6aa68d0b","tid":1124570,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T10:05:01.000Z","msg":"第一次俾人捉到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下世小心啲"},{"pid":"0df250a22bab08985520fc3be903521320f12c48","tid":1124570,"uid":170365,"like":0,"dislike":